// ===== 공통 유틸리티: qs, qsa (절대 삭제/수정 금지) =====
// 단일 ID 선택: qs('lf-budget') → document.getElementById('lf-budget')
const qs = (id) => document.getElementById(id);
// CSS 선택자 그대로 전달: qsa('.some-class'), qsa('[data-i18n]') 등
const qsa = (sel) => document.querySelectorAll(sel);
// ===== ICAG Ladder — UI Logic =====

// Helpers (resolved lazily)
const _fmtUSDT = (n) => (window.formatUSDT || ((v) => Number(v||0).toLocaleString('en-US', {minimumFractionDigits:2, maximumFractionDigits:2})))(n);
const _toast = (m, t) => (window.showToast || ((msg) => console.log(msg)))(m, t);

// ★ [2026-04-25 부모 요청] 코인명 클릭 → Bybit 거래창 (한 창 재사용)
// 같은 name 지정하면 동일 창 재사용 + 포커스. 여러 클릭해도 창 하나만.
function openBybitTrade(market) {
  if (!market) return;
  const sym = String(market).toUpperCase();
  const symbol = sym.endsWith('USDT') ? sym : sym + 'USDT';
  const url = `https://www.bybit.com/trade/usdt/${symbol}`;
  try {
    const win = window.open(url, 'bybit_trade_window');
    if (win) win.focus();
  } catch (e) {
    console.warn('openBybitTrade failed:', e);
  }
}
window.openBybitTrade = openBybitTrade;  // global 노출

function updateLadderOrderAmount(from) {
  const budgetInput = qs('lf-budget');
  const stepsInput = qs('lf-steps');
  const orderInput = qs('lf-fixed-order-usdt');
  const minWarn = qs('lf-min-warn');
  const MIN_ORDER_USDT = 5;
  if (!budgetInput || !stepsInput || !orderInput) return;
  let budget = Number(budgetInput.value) || 0;
  let steps = Math.max(1, Math.floor(Number(stepsInput.value) || 1));
  let perOrder = Math.floor(Number(orderInput.value) || 0);

  if (from === 'budget' || from === 'steps') {
    if (budget > 0 && steps > 0) {
      perOrder = Math.floor(budget / steps / 1000) * 1000;
      if (perOrder > 0 && perOrder < MIN_ORDER_USDT) {
        perOrder = MIN_ORDER_USDT;
        budget = perOrder * steps;
        budgetInput.value = budget;
      }
      orderInput.value = perOrder > 0 ? perOrder : '';
    }
  } else if (from === 'order') {
    if (perOrder > 0 && steps > 0) {
      if (perOrder < MIN_ORDER_USDT) {
        perOrder = MIN_ORDER_USDT;
        orderInput.value = perOrder;
      }
      budget = perOrder * steps;
      budgetInput.value = budget;
    }
  }
  if (minWarn) {
    if (perOrder > 0 && perOrder < MIN_ORDER_USDT) minWarn.classList.remove('d-none');
    else minWarn.classList.add('d-none');
  }
}

function bindLadderFormEvents() {
  const bindMulti = (el, fn) => { if (!el) return; el.addEventListener('input', fn); el.addEventListener('change', fn); };
  bindMulti(qs('lf-budget'), () => updateLadderOrderAmount('budget'));
  bindMulti(qs('lf-steps'), () => updateLadderOrderAmount('steps'));
  bindMulti(qs('lf-fixed-order-usdt'), () => updateLadderOrderAmount('order'));
  updateLadderOrderAmount('budget');
}

// --- ICAG Diagnostics Loader ---
async function loadIcagDiagnostics(market) {
  try {
    const url = market
      ? `/api/ladder/icag/diagnostics?market=${encodeURIComponent(market)}`
      : '/api/ladder/icag/diagnostics';
    const _fetch = (window.AutocoinUtils && window.AutocoinUtils.authFetch)
      ? window.AutocoinUtils.authFetch
      : (u) => fetch(u, { credentials: 'include' });
    const res = await _fetch(url);
    if (!res.ok) return null;
    return await res.json();
  } catch (e) { console.error('ICAG diag error:', e); return null; }
}

async function refreshIcagMarketList() {
  const tbody = qs('icag-market-list');
  if (!tbody) return;
  const data = await loadIcagDiagnostics();
  if (!data || !data.ok) {
    tbody.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan="11" class="text-center text-muted">No ICAG markets</td></tr>';
    return;
  }
  const markets = data.markets || {};
  if (!Object.keys(markets).length) {
    tbody.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan="11" class="text-center text-muted">활성 ICAG 마켓 없음</td></tr>';
    return;
  }
  const zoneBadge = (z) => ({ CORE: 'bg-success', EXPANSION: 'bg-warning', RISK_CUT: 'bg-danger' }[z] || 'bg-secondary');
  const biasBadge = (b) => ({ BUY: 'bg-primary', SELL: 'bg-warning text-dark', BALANCED: 'bg-info' }[b] || 'bg-secondary');
  const uwBadge = (u) => ({ NORMAL: '', DEFENSIVE: 'bg-warning', DCA_RESCUE: 'bg-danger', CAPITULATION: 'bg-dark' }[u] || '');

  tbody.innerHTML = Object.entries(markets).map(([sym, d]) => {
    const pnl = d.realized_pnl || 0;
    const pnlClass = pnl > 0 ? 'text-success' : (pnl < 0 ? 'text-danger' : '');
    const uw = d.underwater_mode || 'NORMAL';
    return `<tr>
      <td><strong>${sym.replace(/USDT$/i,'')}</strong></td>
      <td><span class="badge ${zoneBadge(d.zone)}">${d.zone || '-'}</span></td>
      <td><span class="badge ${biasBadge(d.bias)}">${d.bias || '-'}</span></td>
      <td>${d.anchor_price ? _fmtUSDT(d.anchor_price) : '-'}</td>
      <td>${d.atr ? d.atr.toFixed(1) : '-'} <small class="text-muted">${d.atr_pct ? d.atr_pct.toFixed(2) + '%' : ''}</small></td>
      <td>${d.inv_ratio != null ? (d.inv_ratio * 100).toFixed(1) + '%' : '-'}</td>
      <td>${uw !== 'NORMAL' ? '<span class="badge ' + uwBadge(uw) + '">' + uw + '</span>' : '<span class="text-muted">-</span>'}</td>
      <td><span class="badge bg-success">${d.open_buy_count || 0}</span> / <span class="badge bg-danger">${d.open_sell_count || 0}</span></td>
      <td>${d.trade_count || 0}</td>
      <td class="${pnlClass}">${_fmtUSDT(pnl)}</td>
      <td>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-info btn-xs" onclick="showIcagDetail('${sym}')"><i class="ti ti-chart-dots"></i></button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-xs ms-1" onclick="icagManualSync('${sym}')"><i class="ti ti-refresh"></i></button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-xs ms-1" onclick="icagCancelAll('${sym}')"><i class="ti ti-x"></i></button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-xs ms-1" onclick="showGridStepsPanel('${sym}')"><i class="ti ti-list-details"></i></button>
      </td>
    </tr>`;
  }).join('');
}

async function showIcagDetail(market) {
  const panel = qs('icag-diagnostics-panel');
  if (!panel) return;
  panel.classList.remove('d-none');
  const data = await loadIcagDiagnostics(market);
  if (!data || !data.ok) return;
  const d = data;
  const cards = qs('icag-diag-cards');
  if (cards) {
    cards.innerHTML = `
      <div class="col-md-3"><div class="card card-sm"><div class="card-body py-2">
        <div class="text-muted small">Anchor</div>
        <div class="fw-bold">${d.anchor_price ? _fmtUSDT(d.anchor_price) : '-'}</div>
      </div></div></div>
      <div class="col-md-2"><div class="card card-sm"><div class="card-body py-2">
        <div class="text-muted small">Zone</div>
        <div><span class="badge ${({'CORE':'bg-success','EXPANSION':'bg-warning','RISK_CUT':'bg-danger'})[d.zone] || 'bg-secondary'}">${d.zone || '-'}</span></div>
      </div></div></div>
      <div class="col-md-2"><div class="card card-sm"><div class="card-body py-2">
        <div class="text-muted small">Bias</div>
        <div><span class="badge ${({'BUY':'bg-primary','SELL':'bg-warning text-dark','BALANCED':'bg-info'})[d.bias] || 'bg-secondary'}">${d.bias || '-'}</span></div>
      </div></div></div>
      <div class="col-md-2"><div class="card card-sm"><div class="card-body py-2">
        <div class="text-muted small">ATR</div>
        <div class="fw-bold">${d.atr ? d.atr.toFixed(1) : '-'} <small>(${d.atr_pct ? d.atr_pct.toFixed(2) : 0}%)</small></div>
      </div></div></div>
      <div class="col-md-3"><div class="card card-sm"><div class="card-body py-2">
        <div class="text-muted small">Inventory</div>
        <div class="fw-bold">${d.inv_ratio != null ? (d.inv_ratio * 100).toFixed(1) : 0}%
          <div class="progress mt-1" style="height:4px"><div class="progress-bar ${d.inv_ratio > 0.65 ? 'bg-danger' : (d.inv_ratio > 0.35 ? 'bg-warning' : 'bg-success')}" style="width:${(d.inv_ratio||0)*100}%"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div></div></div>
    `;
  }
  // Fill history
  const fillTbody = qs('icag-fill-history');
  if (fillTbody) {
    const fills = (d.fill_history || []).slice(-20).reverse();
    if (fills.length) {
      fillTbody.innerHTML = fills.map(f => {
        const ts = f.ts ? new Date(f.ts * 1000).toLocaleString('ko-KR', {hour12:false, month:'2-digit', day:'2-digit', hour:'2-digit', minute:'2-digit', second:'2-digit'}) : '-';
        const sideClass = f.side === 'buy' ? 'text-success' : 'text-danger';
        return `<tr>
          <td class="small">${ts}</td>
          <td class="${sideClass}">${(f.side||'').toUpperCase()}</td>
          <td>${_fmtUSDT(f.price || 0)}</td>
          <td>${(f.qty || 0).toFixed(4)}</td>
          <td>${f.profit != null ? _fmtUSDT(f.profit) : '-'}</td>
        </tr>`;
      }).join('');
    } else {
      fillTbody.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan="5" class="text-center text-muted">체결 내역 없음</td></tr>';
    }
  }
}

async function icagManualSync(market) {
  try {
    const af = (window.AutocoinUtils || {}).authFetch || ((u,o) => fetch(u, {credentials:'include', ...o}));
    const res = await af(`/api/ladder/icag/sync?market=${encodeURIComponent(market)}`, {method:'POST'});
    const data = await res.json();
    if (data.ok) _toast(`ICAG sync: ${market}`, 'success');
    else _toast(`Sync failed: ${data.error || ''}`, 'error');
    refreshIcagMarketList();
  } catch (e) { _toast(`Sync error: ${e.message}`, 'error'); }
}

async function icagCancelAll(market) {
  if (!confirm(`Cancel all ICAG orders and remove grid for ${market}?`)) return;
  try {
    const af = (window.AutocoinUtils || {}).authFetch || ((u,o) => fetch(u, {credentials:'include', ...o}));
    const res = await af(`/api/ladder/icag/cancel-all?market=${encodeURIComponent(market)}&remove=true`, {method:'POST'});
    const data = await res.json();
    if (data.ok) _toast(`Canceled ${data.canceled} orders for ${market}${data.removed ? ' (grid removed)' : ''}`, 'success');
    refreshIcagMarketList();
  } catch (e) { _toast(`Cancel error: ${e.message}`, 'error'); }
}

document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  if (qs('lf-budget') && qs('lf-steps') && qs('lf-fixed-order-usdt')) {
    bindLadderFormEvents();
  }
  // ICAG refresh button
  const refreshBtn = qs('btn-icag-refresh-all');
  if (refreshBtn) refreshBtn.addEventListener('click', refreshIcagMarketList);
});
